hotkeycontent:
Undo 						Ctrl + Z
Redo 						Ctrl + Y
Save 						Ctrl + S
Copy Selected				Ctrl + C
Delete Selected				Delete
Play 						Space
Stop (Return to start)  		Release Space
Stop (Don't return) 			Q
Switch Start/Stop 				Same as above
Range Select					Ctrl + R
<size=24>When 'Click to Create' enabled and select one Arc
	Switch Void					F1
	Switch Color					F2
	Switch Type（S<-->B i<-->o)		F3	
	Switch Type（Roll）				F4
</size>

Usage:
1.Input new TimingGroup ID at top bar
2.Edit notes' TimingGroup fields to new ID
3.Edit TimingList of new TimingGroup ID at right bar
4.DO NOT edit note's TimingGroup field to ID that doesn't exist!
